item.title: How do i make emote tabs teleport you when you click on them
item.dc:creator: @delta delta
item.description:
@delta wrote:

search for

	public void update()

and you’ll see all the send frames…

add this with them

sendFrame126("@gre@Home", 180);

then search for

case 130: //close interface println_debug("Closing Interface"); break;
under it add

case 168: if(teleblock) { sendMessage("You are currently teleblocked and cannot tele!"); } else if (!teleblock) { sendMessage("You teleport to home!"); teleportToX = xxxx; teleportToY = yyyy; } break;

that was for the first emote
